<color=#bfbfbf>A Hilichurlian poem created by Ella Musk. According to her, this Recital of Friendship is the work of many hands. Still, you can't help but feel that something sounds a bit off when you read it...</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Olah! Olah!</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Yoyo mosi mita!</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Nye, nye mosi mita,</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Yeye mosi gusha!</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Mosi gusha, mosi tiga,</color>
<color=#bfbfbf>Yeye kucha kucha!</color>
